* others
each time a switch is made from kernel mode to user mode, 
arch-specific: entry.S -> do_siganl()
{ 
        get_signal_deliver()
        {
                if fatal -> do_greoup_exit()->...__cleanup_sighand()
        }

        handle_signal() -> k->u(hanle)-sigreturn->k
}

